flowchart TD
    Start[Telomere Ready for Division] --> AttritionPhase[-45 bp + oxidative]
    AttritionPhase --> hTERTCheck{hTERT > 0.001?}
    hTERTCheck -->|No| NoExtension[0 repeats]
    hTERTCheck -->|Yes| TRF1Gate{n_TRF1 ≥ 400?}
    TRF1Gate -->|Yes| Blocked[TRF1 Gate Closed]
    TRF1Gate -->|No| TERRAFactor[TERRA modulation]
    TERRAFactor --> ActivityCalc[Activity calc + G4 cap]
    ActivityCalc --> FloorCheck{Activity ≥ 0.005?}
    FloorCheck -->|No| Blocked
    FloorCheck -->|Yes| POT1Boost[POT1 5× boost]
    POT1Boost --> AddRepeats[Poisson repeats]
    AddRepeats --> HardCap[Clip @ 7200 bp]
    HardCap --> Sealing[CST fill-in]
    Sealing --> NextDivision[Next cycle]
    Blocked --> NextDivision
    NextDivision --> Start